---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import { siteInfo } from "../../config/siteInfo";
---

<Layout
    title="Legal Notice – Gehringer Consulting"
    description="Legal notice for the Gehringer Consulting website, led by Philippe Gehringer."
>
    <Header slot="header" />

    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-gray-700">
        <h1 class="font-logo text-5xl text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
            Legal Notice
        </h1>

        <!-- Website Publisher -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Website Publisher</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The website <strong>gehringer.fr</strong> is published by:
            <br />
            <strong>Gehringer Consulting</strong> — a consultancy firm specialized
            in transition management, strategy, innovation, and ecological transition.
            <br />
            <strong>Managing Director:</strong> Philippe Gehringer
            <br />
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a
                href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900 transition"
                >{siteInfo.email}</a
            >
            <br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +33 6 14 36 53 77
            <br />
            <strong>Registered Office:</strong> Suresnes (France)
        </p>

        <!-- Legal Status -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Legal Status</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Gehringer Consulting is a <strong
                >SAS (Société par Actions Simplifiée)</strong
            > registered in France.
            <br />
            <strong>SIREN No.:</strong> 948 327 267
            <br />
            <strong>Intra-community VAT Number:</strong> FR40948327267
            <br />
            <strong>APE Code:</strong> 7022Z — Business and other management consultancy
        </p>

        <!-- Hosting -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Hosting</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The website is hosted in Europe by:
            <br />
            <strong>Netlify, Inc.</strong>
            <br />
            2325 3rd Street, Suite 296
            <br />
            San Francisco, CA 94107, USA
            <br />
            <a
                href="https://www.netlify.com"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900">www.netlify.com</a
            >
        </p>

        <!-- Intellectual Property -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            All content on the site (<strong
                >texts, images, graphics, logo, icons</strong
            >), as well as its structure, are the exclusive property of Philippe
            Gehringer, unless explicitly stated otherwise. Any reproduction,
            distribution, or modification without prior authorization is
            prohibited.
        </p>

        <!-- Personal Data -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Personal Data</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            This site does not collect personal data without explicit consent.
            The only information transmitted is what you voluntarily provide via
            contact methods (email or LinkedIn). This information is never
            resold or shared with third parties.
            <br /><br />
            In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you
            can exercise your rights of access, rectification, or deletion by writing
            to:
            <a
                href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900 transition"
                >{siteInfo.email}</a
            >.
        </p>

        <!-- Liability -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Gehringer Consulting strives to ensure the reliability and accuracy
            of the information published. However, errors or omissions may
            occur. The user acknowledges using this information under their
            exclusive responsibility.
        </p>

        <!-- Eco-design -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">
            7. Eco-design and Responsible Hosting
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The site was designed with digital sobriety and environmental
            optimization in mind. The technologies used (Astro, Netlify hosting)
            aim to minimize the carbon footprint associated with browsing the
            pages.
        </p>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
            For any questions regarding the content or legal notice of this
            site, you can write to:
            <a
                href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900 transition"
                >{siteInfo.email}</a
            >.
        </p>

        <!-- Back Button -->
        <div class="text-center mt-16">
            <a
                href="/en"
                class="inline-block bg-gray-900 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-700 transition"
            >
                Back to Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
